result.adr_address: 28 Kimberley Rd, Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 28 Kimberley Rd, Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong
result.name: The Kimberley Hotel

reviews.text:
Definitely would not consider this to be a 4 Star hotel...the location is the best part about the hotel.

It's quite an old building, the bathroom layout is AWFUL; the shower/bathtub doesn't seal which means the water goes EVERYWHERE when you bathe!, to get into the shower you must close the bathroom door, the beds are fairly firm, borderline too firm to sleep on, the power points are in odd locations in the room (and unlike most new hotels you'll need an adapter), the aircon/heating is hard to find the right temperature for; it's either too cold or too warm, the quilt itself even is quite thin and the pillows are very flat...oh...and to get to the floor to exit the building...there are only 2 elevators that access it from the rooms! Only plus side besides location...the room itself is fairly spacious once you get past the bed towards the window.
I stayed here. Good place to stay. Rooms are well maintened. Location is very good. Spa is very good.

Spacious enough and affordable. Smell of the room isn’t as pleasant, lobby is always packed, busy though their staffs have been rushing mad.

Good price, lots of other shops around within walking distance to food, 7-11, SASA cosmetics etc.

If you don’t expect much, I would say it’s a 3.5 star hotel instead.

Old but location is really good. Near to MTR stations, to malls, to avenue of stars, a lot of good restaurants and of course, walking distance to jollibee. 

Bath tub drains so slowly tho.

Absolutely appalling to hear about the service shown to my mum who stayed here. A friend had paid in full for my mum’s accommodation and when she had arrived to check in, the man at the front desk demanded a $1,000 deposit to which she patiently replied that she did not own a credit card, and could not do so. The man impatiently insisted for her to hurry up and pay but it seems that information that she just said to him was going in one ear and out the other. How can she pay when she has no money to pay with? And why wasn’t this information relayed to my mum’s friend? 
He apparently got fed up and flippantly told her “never mind then” - why are you even working at a hotel bro. You’re the first point of physical customer service that travelers see and converse with - is it that hard to be nice? You’re lucky I wasn’t there to experience the disrespect you had shown her. 
He apparently then dropped the key in front of her and pointed to the elevator and said “this is your key. There is the elevator”. Unreal. If you hate your job that much then find a new one - you’re working in the hospitality industry - it’s your job to look after customers and to be hospitable.  
In addition, my mum said that the rooms smelt disgusting - and this is the something I’ve read in a few reviews already - so this might mean that you should actually get down to working on it? 
Also reading a few reviews about the man at the front desk so might be the same one. 
If the reviews went from 0-6 I’d pick 0.

result.name: 君怡閣中菜廳

reviews.text:
飲茶で朝食することにしました。
この店に来るのは10数年ぶりです。
10時半過ぎになってしまったせいか、来店客は我々ともう一組だけでした。
烏龍茶のほか、小籠包や焼豚腸粉など4品を注文。
店の女性スタッフは無愛想ですが、ベテランだったので手際は良いです。
値段はけっこう高めですが、値段相応においしかったです。
代金は合計4300円ほどでした。

精緻的廣東菜愈來愈難在香港吃到。這間餐廳十多年前已開始來吃點心午餐，及小菜晚餐。
一段時間没來，難得這2次來，食物質素，環境及服務皆維持水準。非常不錯。
肥美的金蠔用柚子蜜煎焗，甘香而清新，味美而不膩。
胡椒雞皮香肉滑，一吃難忘。
鮑汁稻庭麵，滑而美味，没有放肉而入味，汁濃而不咸，非常值得一試。
馬拉糕易做難精，這間難得的出色。真心覺得必吃的甜品。
非常美味而滿足的一餐。😍😍
Authentic and delicious food with a reasonable price. Service is always great.
Traditional Cantonese food restaurant. Michelin recommended but I think it's underrated.
這間中菜廳的點心非常美味，食物材料新鮮，價錢中上。很適合大顆人一起聚舊，閒話家常。

result.adr_address: 香港尖沙咀金巴利道28號
result.formatted_address: 香港尖沙咀金巴利道28號
result.name: 君怡酒店

reviews.text: 食落有驚喜👍😘

私の香港宿泊の定番ホテル。
九龍駅から無料送迎バスがあるのでこれを利用するといいです。
K4のバスにのってラックスマナーホテル前のバス停で降りるとすぐです。
14時過ぎはチェックインで大変込み合うのでご注意ください。
部屋はまあまあですがビジネス用途での宿泊ですので特に不満はありません。バスタブがあるのがうれしいです。
他の部屋にあるかはわかりませんが部屋にusbの充電器が設置されていたのがありがたいです。
TVは18chがNHKです。
ロケーションはどこに行くにも大変便利でコンビニやレストランも近く便利、朝食はホテルで食べたことがありません。
香港人の友人が言うのにテナントの中華レストランは有名なお店だそうです。機会があれば食べてみたいです。

入住時工作人員告知公司已付所有費用，給我們倆10張早餐券，
五日之後，要 check out 時說公司只付先生早餐，我要付五天早餐費用高達一千多元港幣，在週日無法與香港公司確認的情況下我們只能付錢趕飛機，有詢問當日入住為何沒說明也無結果，但有被香港旅館欺騙搶劫的感覺。
以後不會再入住此旅館，事實上，心情壞到拒絕香港公司以後的邀約。
